channel.title: Server Download Help Please
channel.description: Hello, I have went to the server downloads section of the forums, and downloaded some of the servers, I was wondering how I could play them. I have winRAR, and heard that I have to extract the .rar file into a folder, I have done that, but I still do not know how to play. Any help would be appreciated.

item.title: Server Download Help Please
item.dc:creator: @Noob_Slayerz Noob Slayerz
item.description:
@Noob_Slayerz wrote:

[quote=“Ch0c0bac0n, post:3, topic:157432”][quote author=Noob Slayerz link=topic=214662.msg1872643#msg1872643 date=1194406588]
Do you want to host your own server or play someone elses. To play someone elses go to moparisthebest.com . The go to moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php look for a server, copy the IP, click file on the webclient and new server. Paste the IP. Then find the Port, copy, file new port paste… Fill out name password enjoy the noobiest guide in world history with terrible grammar
[/quote]
Ok, I understood everything you said, but when I go to the webclient it is just a white square with a red X in the corner, can you help me?[/quote]

I can’t remember how to fix this. So, download the client…

http://www.moparisthebest.com/moparscape.html

Reply to this when you are finished and or need help. It will say download from here here or here or something like that. Just click anyone.
